<div class="container">
  <div class="hero-unit">
    <h1>Hello, readers!</h1>
    <br>
    <p>Looking for a good book? Want to find out what your friends are reading? Sure, you do! 
    <br>
    Start off the new year with a resolution to read more. Forget the gym, exercise that big brain of yours by reading more. Good Books can help you. Add books you want to read in the 'Want to read' bookshelf, then move it to 'Read' when you're finished. We keep you honest! </p>
    <br>
    <p><a href="sign_up" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Sign Up &raquo;</a></p>

    <div class='search_button'>
      <%= form_tag("/search", method: "get") do %>
        <%= label_tag(:query, "Search for books:") %>
        <%= text_field_tag(:query, params[:query]) %>
        <%= submit_tag("Search") %>
      <% end %> 
    </div>
  </div>

